Quirke - Series 1, Episode 3




Elegy for April

A year has passed since the end of Silver Swan. Phoebe is forging a new life for herself with the help of a group of oddly assorted friends. She is worried that her friend April hasn't been heard from in over a week. Lonely and desperate for deeper connections in her life, Phoebe asks Quirke for help, and Quirke, eager to reconnect with his daughter and to keep his own demons at bay is quick to give it.




Original Air Date: 02-Mar-2014
